headline: Interactive Brokers Group to Host Third Quarter Earnings Conference Call
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., September 25, 2025--Interactive Brokers Group, Inc. (Nasdaq: IBKR) plans to announce its third quarter financial results on Thursday, October 16, 2025, in a release that will be issued at approximately 4:00 pm (ET). The press release will also be available on the company's website, www.interactivebrokers.com/ir.
